law.text:
The Department shall:
help veterans and their dependents to receive promptly and regularly all of the benefits to which veterans or dependents are entitled under federal law;
help veterans and their dependents in:
preparing, in proper form, claims for benefits;
presenting the claims to the appropriate governmental unit;
trying to prevent and to relieve congestion in the processing of the claims; and
obtaining and expediting action on the claims; and
on request, provide a veteran with a document certifying veteran status.
